      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? This beauty is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stayed spotless inside and out. It\u2019s such a smooth, reliable ride and I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
