    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 that exemplifies mechanical perfection. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, breathing through six individual throttle bodies and mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis integrity is verified with documented subframe reinforcement, and the critical VANOS system has been professionally overhauled. Power is delivered to the asphalt via a factory variable M differential lock. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, with rod bearing replacement already addressed. This is a turn-key, zero-compromise driver for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
